<HEADLINE> China Releases Slogans for 50th Anniversary (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 13 (Xinhua) -- The General Office of the
Central Committee of the Chinese Communist Party (CPC) and the
General Office of the State Council today released 50 slogans for
the 50th anniversary of the founding of the People's Republic of
China, which falls on October 1.
</P>
<P>
They are:
</P>
<P>
1. Warmly celebrate the 50th anniversary of the founding of the
People's Republic of China!
</P>
<P>
2. Warmly hail the great successes in China's reform and
opening up and socialist modernization drive!
</P>
<P>
3. Strive to build China into a prosperous, powerful,
democratic and culturally advanced socialist country!
</P>
<P>
4. Hold high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory and put
forward the cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics into the 21st century!
</P>
<P>
5. Hold high the great banner of Deng Xiaoping Theory, and
adhere to arming the Party and educating the people with Deng
Xiaoping theory!
</P>
<P>
6. Take economic development as the central task, adhere to the
Four Cardinal Principles, reform and opening up!
</P>
<P>
7. Seize the current opportunity, continue the reform, open
China wider to the outside world, promote development and maintain
stability!
</P>
<P>
8. Emancipate the mind, seek truth from facts and firmly
promote reform and opening up!
</P>
</TEXT>
