<HEADLINE> Thai Bourse Up 14.03 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BANGKOK, September 13 (Xinhua) -- The Stock Exchange of
Thailand (SET) index Monday gained 14.03 points from last Friday
to close at 444.94.
</P>
<P>
Some 476 million shares worth 8.17 billion baht (220.8 million
U.S. dollars) changed hands Monday.
</P>
<P>
The SET index closed at 430.91 on Friday, down 0.17 points from
the previous session. 
</P>
</TEXT>
