EREZ CHECKPOINT (ISRAEL), September 13 (Xinhua) -- Israel and
Palestine officially launched the final-status talks in a ceremony
held here Monday evening. Secretary General of the Executive
Committee of the Palestinian Liberation Organization Mahmoud
Abbas, also known as Abu Mazan, headed the Palestinian delegation
