<TEXT>
<P>
18. Adhere to and improve the system of regional ethnic
autonomy, consolidate and develop the socialist nationality
relationship of equality, unity, mutual assistance and realize the
common prosperity of all nationalilties!
</P>
<P>
19. Rely on the working class whole-heartedly!
</P>
<P>
20. Self-reliance, hard work, build the country with thrift, do
every undertaking with thrift!
</P>
<P>
