<HEADLINE> Angola to Holst 22nd African Inter-parliamentary </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LUANDA, September 13 (Xinhua) -- The 22nd Conference of the
African Inter-Parliamentary Union (AIPU) to be held in Luanda is a
good opportunity for African lawmakers to know Angola, Angola's
parliament speaker said here Monday.
</P>
<P>
Chairman of the Angolan National Assembly Roberto de Almeida
made the remarks at the opening ceremony of the 36th session of
the AIPU Executive Committee, which is now making preparations for
the two-day African inter-parliamentary conference to be held on
Friday.
