legally established institutions, he said.
</P>
<P>
"We don't accept that one party can have a private army,"
Almeida stressed, adding that the Angolan army has the mission of
defending the national sovereignty and guaranteeing the security
of the population.
</P>
<P>
As for the Friday meeting of the African inter-parliamentary
conference, the chairman said that the event is important for
exchanging opinions among parliaments in African countries.
</P>
