<HEADLINE> Jayson Williams to Have Knee Surgery </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, September 14 (Xinhua) -- NBA Nets center Jayson
Williams, who is battling to return from a career-threatening leg
injury, will have more surgey on his right knee today.
</P>
