in Jerusalem, "especially in this year of intensive discussions
on the permanent status agreement," Prime Minister Ehud Barak
declared in Jerusalem Monday. As his first step in this
direction, Barak summoned the Ministerial Committee on Jerusalem
to its first meeting. But he insisted that the meeting was "not
