Athletics Association, predicted "good results from the women's 1,
500m, 5,000m and 10,000m races."
</P>
<P>
But, the Chinese athletics chief was quick to add that "the
overall level of comptition is not expected to be high enough as
the City Games was conceived as a cradle for young athletes with
potentials as only those under 20 are eligible."
</P>
<P>
