<HEADLINE> Investor Education Program to Be Launched in HK Schools </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As part of their efforts, the SFC has sponsored a theater
company to produce an interactive drama entitled "Don't guess when
you invest." The drama will be performed at 50 secondary schools.
</P>
<P>
The focus of this education campaign, which targets students in
the upper forms, is to foster a correct attitude in investing
among future investors by promoting understanding of the risks and
rewards of the financial markets.
</P>
