of Moscow, a new attack killed 73 people on Monday in the Russian
metropolis. Russian Interior Minister Vladimir Rouchailo accused
the Islamic rebels of Dagestan of staging the attacks and most
observers consider the Russian Caucasus as the hotbed of terrorism.
</P>
<P>
-- Israelis and Palestinians resumed Monday evening in Erez
their talks on the final status of the Palestinian territories.
The two sides apparently don't have the intention to yield on the
problem of the status of Jerusalem and frontier lines. 
