<HEADLINE> Australia Prepares for Aid Drops to East Timor </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
CANBERRA, September 14 (Xinhua) -- Emergency aid drops to East
Timor will not begin before Wednesday as AusAID is finalizing its
decision on an appropriate aircraft and crew.
</P>
