the upper and middle reaches of the Yangtze and Yellow rivers and
restore the ecological system in the areas in five to ten years,
Chinese Premier Zhu Rongji stressed recently.
</P>
<P>
During an inspection tour of southwest China's Sichuan Province
from September 6 to 12, Zhu Rongji investigated the forest
protection project in the province.
</P>
